				\begin{document}$$\text{ClST}-150\hspace{0.17em}=\hspace{0.17em}\text{DSA x Qef}$$\end{document}ClST-150=DSA x Qef

The DSA was calculated as the ratio of linezolid concentration evaluated in effluent flow (Cef) over the amount reported in after (Cpre) and before (Cpost) filter samples, according to the following formula:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
